{"tid":2256455,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鎮幹部稱「刁民太多」惹公憤","createTime":"2020-10-24T11:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T12:39:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a82e6a476413a6c1b3aee753143a59777cf66e0d","tid":2256455,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:14:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201024/X7VB5CIN6RG65IRGOIX26YRDOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201024%2FX7VB5CIN6RG65IRGOIX26YRDOI%2F&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLPbhcgmijv%2F0DJBpEVBRbRs%3D&h=11669ab4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201024%2FX7VB5CIN6RG65IRGOIX26YRDOI%2F&h=fa85906b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201024/X7VB5CIN6RG65IRGOIX26YRDOI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n鎮幹部稱「刁民太多」惹公憤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Sva-d7mCq68GhfUfaiRhiDDRb10=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EUJOIQAUV5DD5BRKCKNLDMO5XM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSva-d7mCq68GhfUfaiRhiDDRb10%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEUJOIQAUV5DD5BRKCKNLDMO5XM.jpg&h=b67dbf99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海南萬寧市萬城鎮一名幹部。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主持人斥胡說八道<br />\n<br />\n這一次「罵刁民」事件源於上周五（16日），海南廣播電視總台《政風行風熱線》接到當地民眾電話，該民眾指自己無法領到其他農民都有的證書，節目便向政府查詢，該名幹部吳珍海接受訪問時，突然炮轟傳媒，稱「現在刁民太多，都是你們這些新聞媒體在支撐他們」，欄目主持人即反擊：「簡直胡說八道﹗你對你說的話負責任嗎？」吳也掛斷電話，連線中他拒絕透露自己的姓名和職務。<br />\n<br />\n直到官方前日通報，指到了本周三（21日），《政風行風熱線》於同日報道吳珍海的言論問題，遂約談吳珍海，並指經查，發現吳的不當言論帶來十分惡劣的影響，已責成他向海南廣播電視總台《政風行風熱線》欄目進行道歉，又請通過欄目組向廣大群眾道歉，並指吳已深刻認識到自己的錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n光明網"},{"pid":"c99f2b53f50c2388e15f1186542cdd6f72b8264f","tid":2256455,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4781b2db900a618026d651f2931dc72fd2d9d9b5","tid":2256455,"uid":39974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:33:46.000Z","msg":"幹部咁講又錯唔哂啵"},{"pid":"90cce5975cd82145223a357f5723cb523c168f9c","tid":2256455,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T12:39:10.000Z","msg":"刁民出狗官丫嘛"}]}